      "rationale": "Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed on 6 input parameters. Blood viscosity inputs drawn from the 2026 Q1 dataset (current). However, the primary hemolysis experimental boundary conditions are sourced from the 2025 Q3 dataset (dataVintage 2025-09-15), which predates the modelRevisionDate of 2026-02-01. Re-validation of model inputs against the revised build is planned for Q2 2026 but has not been completed. This temporal mismatch limits confidence that the stale experimental inputs remain representative of the revised model's assumptions. Achieved level 2."
